#[tokio::main]
async fn main() -> Result<(), Error> {
    let (region, client, bucket_name, file_name, key, target_key) = initialize_variables().await;

    if let Err(e) = run_s3_operations(region, client, bucket_name, file_name, key, target_key).await
    {
        println!("{:?}", e);
    };

    Ok(())
}
